
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Food Menu</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">

    <header style="background-color: #333; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <h1>Delicious Restaurant</h1>
        <p>Explore Our Tasty Menu</p>
    </header>

    <section style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: space-around; padding: 20px;">

        <article style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 10px; width: 300px;">
            <img src="burger.jpg" alt="Burger" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Burger</h2>
            <p>Delicious beef burger with lettuce, tomatoes, and cheese.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold; color: #e44d26;">$8.99</p>
        </article>

        <article style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 10px; width: 300px;">
            <img src="pizza.jpg" alt="Pizza" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Pizza</h2>
            <p>Classic Margherita pizza with fresh mozzarella and basil.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold; color: #e44d26;">$10.99</p>
        </article>

        <!-- Add more menu items as needed -->

    </section>

    <footer style="background-color: #333; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 10px; position: fixed; bottom: 0; width: 100%;">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Delicious Restaurant. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
